<section
    id="contact"
    aria-label="Section with information about how to contact me"
>

    <div>
        <h2>Contact <span class="pattern">happens</span></h2>

        <p>
            Like most wild
            <b>Designerus millenius</b>, I can be easily spooked with phone
            calls, as they are strongly associated with one of our primal
            predators, the
            <b>Telemarketerus obnoscius</b>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Good old email is a safer bet, so use just use the form to
            reach me!
        </p>
        <p>
            Or just find me on
            <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/menosketiago/"
                rel="noopener"
                target="_blank"
            >LinkedIn</a>, maybe ðŸ˜œ
        </p>
    </div>

    <form
        action="https://formspree.io/xyyyddgr"
        method="POST"
        role="form"
        aria-label="A form you can use to contact me"
    >
        <div class="input">
            <input
                type="text"
                name="name"
                id="name"
                minlength="1"
                maxlength="100"
                required
                autocomplete="name"
                aria-label="Type your name or alias"
                
            />
            <label for="name" aria-hidden="true">Name</label>
        </div>

        <div class="input">
            <input
                type="email"
                name="email"
                id="email"
                minlength="5"
                maxlength="254"
                required
                autocomplete="email"
                aria-label="Type your email address"
            />
            <label for="email" aria-hidden="true">Email</label>
        </div>

        <div class="input">
            <textarea
                name="message"
                id="message"
                maxlength="2500"
                required
                aria-label="Write your message here"
            ></textarea>
            <label for="message" aria-hidden="true">Drop some lines here...</label>
        </div>

        <button
            id="btn-submit-message"
            class="btn arrow-right"
            type="submit"
            aria-label="Send message"
        >Send Message</button>
    </form>
</section>